metadata.name: Marine Blues Re:boot Club #1
metadata.description:
Marine Blues Re:boot Club(MBRC) is a Ethererum based PFP NFT project that rebooted the first generation Webtoon Marine Blues.
The team behind the MBRC project is OGQ, a social creator platform that has 1million creators with 17 million users registered and 4 million monthly visitors.
We plan to share profits generated from the businesses listed in our roadmap with our holders, and host numerous online/offline events to go global.

Starfish, Octopus, Webfoot Octopus, Sea Urchin and Sea Squirt!
We invite you to a journey of 5 MBRC friends once again to become the stars in the sky!
